Class Summary
Attachment A flexible container for data that can be attached to other pPOD attachees.
AttachmentNamespace To prevent name clashes among AttachmentTypes.
AttachmentType Says what kind of attachment we have.
Character A standard character.
CharacterState A stateNumber of a Character.

CharacterStateCell A cell in a CharacterStateMatrix.
CharacterStateMatrix A standard matrix - aka a character matrix.
CharacterStateRow Rows of a CharacterStateMatrix.
DNACharacter  
DNAState  
OTU Operational Taxonomic Unit.
OTUSet A set of OTUs.
PersistentObject Base class for edu.upenn.cis.ppod.model (and subpackages) entities.

PPodVersionInfoInterceptor Assign a new PPodVersionInfo to any PPodEntitys that are marked as being newly saved or modified and to any null members of CharacterStateMatrix.getColumnPPodVersionInfos()
Study A collection of work - inspired by a Mesquite project - sets of OTU sets and, through the OTU sets, matrices and tree sets.
Tree A phylogenetic tree.
TreeSet A tree set.
